2026-05-16T02:45:00.5414964Z 226            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T02:45:00.5415765Z 227            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T02:45:00.5416465Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T02:45:00.5417167Z 229            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T02:45:00.5418002Z 230            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T02:45:00.5418792Z 231            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T02:45:00.5419555Z 232            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
