2026-05-16T02:45:01.0984497Z 21    <!--
2026-05-16T02:45:01.0984811Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-16T02:45:01.0984980Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-16T02:45:01.0985268Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-16T02:45:01.0985530Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-16T02:45:01.0985800Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-16T02:45:01.0986065Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-16T02:45:01.0986347Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-16T02:45:01.0986621Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-16T02:45:01.0986888Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-16T02:45:01.0987120Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-16T02:45:01.0987458Z 32    -->
2026-05-16T02:45:01.0987813Z 33    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
