2026-05-16T02:45:01.1045183Z 51    <!--
2026-05-16T02:45:01.1045567Z 52        Foreground service used to keep the Pomodoro countdown alive when
2026-05-16T02:45:01.1045922Z 53        the app is backgrounded. Without this, a viewModelScope coroutine
2026-05-16T02:45:01.1046276Z 54        is cancelled as soon as the user switches apps and the completion
2026-05-16T02:45:01.1046972Z 55        notification is never shown. The timer is declared as a
2026-05-16T02:45:01.1047364Z 56        mediaPlayback foreground service because Samsung One UI suppresses
2026-05-16T02:45:01.1047705Z 57        FOREGROUND_SERVICE_SPECIAL_USE notifications, preventing the
